"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/391331","Department for Transport","false","2015-07-23","<p>The Government have no plans to introduce regulations to restrict high intensity lit advertising over motorways for goods and services at this time.</p>",,"Lord Ahmad of Wimbledon",,"2015-07-23T16:26:40.61Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/391331/answer","Biography information for Lord Ahmad of Wimbledon","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/391331/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/391331/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2015-07-20","Motorways: Outdoor Advertising","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government what regulations they are considering to restrict high intensity lit advertising for goods and services over motorways in urban locations.","false","Biography information for Lord Moonie",,"Lord Moonie","HL1671"
